{"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "title": "Shin Seiki Evangelion", "title_uuid": "cc3209cd-c119-4870-b06c-9a34f447db7e", "volume": "Shin Seiki Evangelion 12", "volume_uuid": "08fab706-06f0-419a-8a19-dbde094a40c9", "pages": [{"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 2005, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [281, 505, 660, 908], "vertical": false, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["当本義行", "子は親を選べなしいと言うけど、私の", "父は運良く尊敬できる人でした。若", "くして逝ってしまい、母親を不幸に", "してしまったことだけ、唯一のマイ", "ナスポイントでしたが．．。考えてみ", "れば、いつもシンジの気持ちになっ", "てネームを描いていいるけど、高校生", "の息子がしいる私は、どちらかと言う", "とゲンドウに近いんだよなあ．．．。", "Ａ．Ｔ．フィールドは張れないけど、身", "勝手な点においいて．．．（爆）"]}, {"box": [289, 1541, 661, 1571], "vertical": false, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["ＣＯＮＫＤＥＲＣＡ／ＫＡＺＵＡＮＴＡＤＡＨＡＲＯ，ＩＢＥＥＮＴＯ"]}, {"box": [892, 15, 1674, 419], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ツッ"]}, {"box": [1657, 550, 1974, 664], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["Ｖｏｌｕｍｅ", "「父と子"]}, {"box": [872, 1470, 1296, 1571], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["こうして、ここでこの２０分以内には５０ｍｍでありましたが、", "原作インフラートＧＡＬＩＮＡと"]}], "img_path": "eva12_001.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1894, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [205, 84, 508, 227], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["９７８４０４７１５４２０９"]}, {"box": [206, 276, 509, 410], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＭａｍＭｉｎＭａｎｄＷｉｎｄｉｎ１９２０９７９００５６００"]}, {"box": [594, 83, 994, 165], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＩＳＢＭ９７８－４－０４－７１５４２０－９", "ＣＯ９７９、¥５６０Ｅ"]}, {"box": [586, 260, 927, 343], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["定価：本体５６０円「税別発行・角川書店"]}, {"box": [585, 261, 930, 341], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["定価：本体５６０円（税別）", "発行・角川書店"]}, {"box": [0, 218, 94, 966], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["新世紀"]}, {"box": [487, 781, 846, 1064], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＮＬ"]}, {"box": [0, 1065, 123, 1494], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["貞本義行", "京乍カブー・", "．．．"]}], "img_path": "eva12_002.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 2396, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [1097, 219, 1256, 1466], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["．．．", "新世紀エヴァンシリアン、軽くしていたのですが、"]}, {"box": [430, 1487, 676, 1504], "vertical": false, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["ＫａｄｏｋｏｕｒｅＣｏｒｍｉｃｓＡ"]}, {"box": [1688, 847, 1966, 883], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＹｏｕＴｕｂｅＴｗｉｔｔｅｒｓａｍａｍｏでの"]}, {"box": [1719, 898, 1916, 933], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["Ｒｈｏｒｍｅ．ｃｏｍｉｎｇｘ"]}], "img_path": "eva12_003.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1091, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [215, 45, 415, 76], "vertical": false, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["ネイセンスに"]}, {"box": [81, 294, 418, 446], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["Ｖｏｌｕｍｅ．", "漫画、夏本まで", "Ｙａｈｏｏ！！Ｔｏｒｋｉｓｔｏｒｏ！", "原作、カラー・ＧＡＮＡＸ"]}], "img_path": "eva12_004.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1098, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [], "img_path": "eva12_005.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1103, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [], "img_path": "eva12_006.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1107, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [234, 159, 792, 339], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＰＰｏＧＲＡＭ"]}, {"box": [389, 339, 697, 380], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＥｖＡＮＧＥＬＣＮ！？"]}, {"box": [212, 439, 720, 496], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳｈａｚｏｐＮｏｔＩＤＦ－"]}, {"box": [215, 557, 530, 606], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["Ｓｍａｍｏ父と子"]}, {"box": [207, 643, 609, 723], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＩＮＥの約束の時"]}, {"box": [845, 546, 931, 823], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["３３５７"]}, {"box": [214, 1108, 505, 1164], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["Ｓｉｎｍａｇｒ呼応"]}, {"box": [209, 770, 631, 946], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["Ｓｍａｚｏｎ避近＿", "ＳＩＣＥＭの空よりの敵一"]}, {"box": [208, 1001, 775, 1059], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＭＥＭ２ＴｈｅＭａｔｉｎｓｔｏｒｔｉｏｎの"]}, {"box": [342, 1248, 530, 1274], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ＧＨＮＬＪＩＫＡＲＩ"]}, {"box": [465, 1386, 695, 1420], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＧＥＮＤＯＨＩＫＡＰＩ"]}], "img_path": "eva12_007.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1109, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [13, 92, 47, 268], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["登場人物紹介"]}, {"box": [90, 242, 465, 298], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["られて育つ。突然、父・ゲンドウによりネルフ", "に呼ばれエヴァのパイロットとなる。（１４歳）"]}, {"box": [251, 178, 465, 193], "vertical": false, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["本編の主人公。１０年以上"]}, {"box": [248, 206, 465, 231], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["もの間、伯父の家に預け"]}, {"box": [251, 345, 395, 373], "vertical": false, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["葛城ミサト"]}, {"box": [693, 123, 748, 182], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["君の手で", "消して", "もらいたい"]}, {"box": [976, 59, 1021, 117], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["だから僕は僕を"]}, {"box": [90, 481, 465, 534], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["の直属の上司にあたる。おおらかな性格で", "シンジを見守る、数少ないい理解者。（２９歳）"]}, {"box": [206, 412, 468, 467], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ネルフ本部戦術作戦部作", "最後の戦局第一課所属。シンジ"]}, {"box": [234, 556, 406, 625], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["碇ゲンドウ"]}, {"box": [89, 718, 465, 771], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.5, "lines": ["任務至上主義で実の息子特にも冷徹だが、レ", "イには不思議な思いいやりを見せる。（４８歳）"]}, {"box": [246, 648, 467, 704], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["シンジの実父。特務機関", "ネルフの最高司令長官。"]}, {"box": [228, 787, 373, 865], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["綾波レイ"]}, {"box": [87, 953, 465, 1010], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.5, "lines": ["って選ばれたファ・ーストチルドレンという以上、", "外の経歴は不明の謎の美少女。（１４歳）"]}, {"box": [246, 887, 467, 942], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.5, "lines": ["零号機のパイロット。マル", "ドゥック機関の報告書によ"]}, {"box": [220, 1017, 463, 1146], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["物流・アスカ・ラングレードイツがちまちますので", "フィングレードイツから来た式号機のパイロット、市脱明は"]}, {"box": [249, 1159, 467, 1179], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["パイロット。頭脳明晰、操"]}, {"box": [513, 528, 1045, 1506], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["●前巻までのあらすじ", "度重なる使徒との戦いやアスカの病神汚染、暴かれたレイの正体によっ", "て心に傷を負ったシンジ。そんな彼と心を通わせたいと願うカラルだ", "が、拒絶されてしまう。その後カラルはゼーレからの命令を受け、ネル", "フ本部に存在するアダムと接触すべく、使徒としての正体を現す。裏切", "られたと感じ、激高するシンジ。彼はせ［ドインパクトが起こるのを阻", "止するために、カラルを追撃する。ついにアダムの元へ到達したカラル", "は、それが。リリス〟であったことこを知る。そしてすべてを悟ったカラル", "は、シンジの手で自らを消してほしいと望むのだった。シンジはそれが彼", "の最後の願いだと聞き、自分の手によって怒めることを選択する。一方、人類補完計画を遂行するため事を", "急ぐゼーレは、ネルフ本部のスーパー「コンビューターマギーのハッキングを行う。しかし、リッコのブロテクト", "作業によって失敗し、ゼーレはネルフおよびエヴァを占拠すべく、戦略自衛隊戦自による武力行使を実行し", "たっかくして戦目の侵攻が始まり、エヴァのパイロットであるシンジ達の命令が狙われることとなったが．．．！？"]}, {"box": [151, 1321, 173, 1354], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["８０１？"]}, {"box": [85, 1190, 467, 1246], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.5, "lines": ["縦センス抜群の美少女だが、使徒の攻撃に", "よって精神汚染を受けけ．．．。（１４歳）"]}, {"box": [93, 1451, 157, 1582], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["分野機関ネルフの", "特例による", "及び指揮権の日本国政府への", "友達です"]}, {"box": [128, 1509, 143, 1575], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["法的保護の破棄"]}, {"box": [368, 1307, 426, 1393], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["先程", "第２東京から", "Ａ１８１が出ました"]}, {"box": [702, 1448, 771, 1548], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["まず", "パイロットが", "狙われるわ"]}, {"box": [924, 1196, 982, 1303], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["レイとアスカの", "安全も早急に", "確保よ"]}, {"box": [940, 1356, 982, 1467], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["連中の本命が", "エヴァの占拠なら"]}], "img_path": "eva12_008.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1102, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [], "img_path": "eva12_009.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1104, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [53, 1483, 681, 1546], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＯＥ．７．ＧＥＮＯＶＩ"]}], "img_path": "eva12_010.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1106, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [], "img_path": "eva12_011.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1105, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [], "img_path": "eva12_012.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1105, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [], "img_path": "eva12_013.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1107, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [], "img_path": "eva12_014.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1103, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [], "img_path": "eva12_015.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1106, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [860, 96, 934, 254], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["全隔壁を", "閉鎖します！"]}, {"box": [510, 332, 625, 518], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["非戦闘員は", "第８７経路にて", "退避して下さい"]}, {"box": [806, 996, 906, 1189], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["地下第３隔壁", "損壊！"]}, {"box": [171, 1198, 259, 1417], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["第２層に", "侵入されました"]}], "img_path": "eva12_016.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1103, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [798, 84, 828, 239], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["アスカは！？"]}, {"box": [960, 601, 997, 753], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["３００号病室です。"]}, {"box": [620, 614, 688, 773], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["グループ４が", "警護してます"]}, {"box": [485, 604, 550, 810], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["かまわないから", "弐号機に乗せて！"]}, {"box": [838, 915, 998, 1070], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["でも", "操縦できる", "状態じゃ", "ありません！！"]}, {"box": [435, 925, 498, 1104], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["アスカ収容後は", "地底湖に隠して"]}, {"box": [306, 962, 371, 1196], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["すぐに見つかるけど", "ケージよりマシだわ"]}, {"box": [189, 912, 241, 1017], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["了解！"]}, {"box": [653, 1248, 718, 1426], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["そこだと確実に", "殺されるわ"]}, {"box": [546, 1246, 610, 1501], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["かくまうにはエヴァの", "中が最適なのよ"]}], "img_path": "eva12_017.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1105, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [933, 118, 1000, 276], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["パイロットの", "投薬を中止"]}, {"box": [848, 167, 917, 278], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["弐号機", "発進準備"]}, {"box": [778, 165, 802, 209], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["！？"]}, {"box": [392, 100, 482, 257], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["位置を確認", "できません"]}, {"box": [417, 388, 480, 545], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["どちらも", "所在不明です"]}, {"box": [956, 1023, 1001, 1209], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["捕捉急いで！"]}, {"box": [531, 715, 649, 923], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["シンジ君と", "レイは！？"]}, {"box": [443, 1268, 483, 1453], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["殺されるわよ"]}], "img_path": "eva12_018.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1105, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [875, 115, 1000, 279], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["戦自", "約一個師団を", "投入か"]}, {"box": [398, 123, 475, 279], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["占拠は時間の", "問題だな"]}, {"box": [440, 396, 464, 473], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["．．．ああ"]}, {"box": [106, 482, 143, 587], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["時は来た"]}], "img_path": "eva12_019.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1105, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [876, 1103, 970, 1290], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["第２グループ", "応答なし"]}, {"box": [848, 1346, 864, 1468], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["いや、いや．．．"]}, {"box": [137, 1307, 243, 1490], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["７７電算室", "連絡不能！"]}], "img_path": "eva12_020.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1108, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [890, 107, 1008, 292], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["５２番の", "リニアレール", "爆破されました"]}, {"box": [693, 106, 731, 237], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["たち悪いな"]}, {"box": [348, 90, 388, 248], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["無理もないわ"]}, {"box": [895, 631, 986, 812], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["パイロット", "収容完了！"]}, {"box": [459, 382, 538, 567], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["使徒の方が", "よっぽどいいよ"]}, {"box": [120, 353, 222, 539], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["みんな人を殺す", "ことに慣れてない", "ものね．．"]}, {"box": [132, 654, 223, 845], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["エヴァ弐号機", "射出します！"]}], "img_path": "eva12_021.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1105, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [879, 1025, 992, 1209], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["８番ルートから", "水深７０に固定", "されます"]}, {"box": [203, 1010, 307, 1168], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["シンジ君は", "まだ見つから", "ないの！？"]}, {"box": [146, 1220, 228, 1435], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["初号機も急いで", "発進させて"]}], "img_path": "eva12_022.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1106, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [876, 121, 991, 329], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["初号機バイロット", "所在位置を", "捕捉しました"]}, {"box": [910, 1010, 991, 1168], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["なぜまだ", "こんな所に"]}, {"box": [568, 996, 675, 1206], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31.0, "lines": ["ルート４７は", "すでに寸断されて", "います"]}, {"box": [295, 995, 323, 1182], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["なんてこと．．．"]}, {"box": [385, 1295, 447, 1447], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["このままでは", "シンジ君が．．．"]}], "img_path": "eva12_023.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1105, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [403, 65, 442, 173], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["冬月先生"]}, {"box": [548, 592, 617, 698], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あとは", "頼みます"]}, {"box": [923, 1068, 994, 1173], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["わかって", "いる"]}, {"box": [565, 1068, 636, 1195], "vertical": true, "font_size": 