ヤングエースにて", "「新世紀エヴァシゲリオン」を連載中。"]}, {"box": [375, 888, 500, 912], "vertical": false, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["Ｔｈｅ，Ａｕｔｈｏｎ"]}, {"box": [374, 952, 482, 976], "vertical": false, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["Ａｓｓｉｓｔａｎｔ"]}, {"box": [469, 825, 643, 853], "vertical": false, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＡＦＦＬＩＳＴ"]}, {"box": [643, 892, 729, 914], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["貞本義行"]}, {"box": [643, 954, 729, 975], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["高橋伸義"]}, {"box": [384, 1109, 725, 1227], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["さりたりな一飯田史様・桂明日香", "コヤマシゲト太田紅美・水原賢治", "益山亮司，長尾圭二佐野久美子", "中山かつみ、長野雄大"]}, {"box": [645, 987, 729, 1039], "vertical": false, "font_size": 19.5, "lines": ["加藤雄一", "催京恩"]}, {"box": [623, 1050, 729, 1067], "vertical": false, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["佐藤竜太郎"]}, {"box": [375, 1297, 728, 1328], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["Ｔｈｅ．Ｏｒｉｇｉｎａｌ／カラー・ＧＡＩＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [487, 1364, 648, 1385], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ａｎｋｓｔｏＭＡＫＯ"]}], "img_path": "eva12_182.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1099, "img_height": 1600, "blocks": [{"box": [462, 464, 609, 485], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ｏｋａｗａＣｏｎ"]}, {"box": [443, 520, 628, 542], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["角川コミックス・エース・"]}, {"box": [309, 554, 697, 684], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["新世紀エヴァンゲリオン◎", "漫画と", "貞本義行"]}, {"box": [426, 692, 664, 715], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["２０１０年４月３日初版発行"]}, {"box": [468, 765, 606, 825], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.5, "lines": ["発行者", "井上伸一郎"]}, {"box": [562, 632, 819, 676], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["カラー・ＧＡＩＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [411, 857, 665, 884], "vertical": false, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["発行・株式会社角川書店"]}, {"box": [226, 890, 851, 915], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["〒１０２：８０７８東京都千代田区富士見２１ほ－３電話，（１０３）２３８－８５４１（編集）"]}, {"box": [370, 1093, 401, 1112], "vertical": false, "fo